window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A man too angry to die. Women too wonderful to ignore.</b><br> <br> After being killed in a home invasion, John Dagan rises in a world of mayhem and magic.<br> <br> In this world, he is the most dangerous thing. And he’s very, very pissed off.<br> <br> John must now make the choice to be this world's destroyer, or savior. Thankfully, he has some strange but cute companions to keep him company…and maybe start a massacre while they're at it.</p>"; 
